 libavcodec-dev (>= 4:0.6~svn20100505-1~), libswscale-dev, libpng12-dev | libpng-dev,
 libjpeg-dev | libjpeg8-dev
Standards-Version: 3.9.4
Homepage: http://code.google.com/p/ffmpegthumbnailer/
